note.p:
Pub. L. 107–171, title VII, § 7502(b), May 13, 2002, 116 Stat. 463, provided that: “The amendments made by subsection (a) [amending this section] shall not affect any basis for distribution of funds by formula (in effect on the date of enactment of this Act [May 13, 2002]) to— “(1) the Federated States of Micronesia;
“(2) the Republic of the Marshall Islands; or
“(3) the Republic of Palau.”
